    <descript>
      <abstract>The State Highway LRS system consists of the Interstate, U.S. and State Highways of Arkansas. Each point represents a Mile Marker reading on stated routes..</abstract>
      <purpose>The purpose of the Mile Marker points is to be able to locate a point on the State Highway System at each mile interval.</purpose>
